android:layout_height="wrap_content"/> 
<Button 
android:id="@+id/btnStop" 
android:text="Stop Music" 
android:layout_width="wrap_content" 
android:layout_height="wrap_content"/> 
</LinearLayout> 
● The Telephone API in Android is used to perform calling functions. It uses Intent actions 
such as ACTION_DIAL to open the dialer and ACTION_CALL to make a direct phone 
call (with required permission). 
MainActivity .kt 
